description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 68, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 68, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Box for East, 1 for South, and 5 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40681-94152-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [68 Votes, Common]
